{"tid":309503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"駕警車撞途人致對方重傷　黑警認不小心駕駛判罰2,000元","createTime":"2017-07-05T05:33:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T13:00:45.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":153,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0b5a236657558779af1a2c609bd6978ef2f98cbd","tid":309503,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T05:33:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170705/large/1499229442_3ec8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170705%2Flarge%2F1499229442_3ec8.jpg&h=f0342fb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告顧嘉能(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n隸屬尖沙咀軍裝巡邏小隊高級警員，去年10月19日深夜11時駕駛警車往尖沙咀寶勒巷處理一宗醉酒人士案件時，於漆咸道麼地道交界將一名橫過馬路的外籍人士撞傷，導致對方頭部及盤骨骨折，並且腦出血。高級警員今承認不小心駕駛罪，今被判罰款2,000元。<br />\n<br />\n41歲被告顧嘉能透過律師求情，指被告已坦白認罪，承認當時專注度不足，有負警隊服務市民的承諾，更令市民受傷，並指今後不能再駕駛警車。律師又指被告未來晉升警長評核必定被覆核，並須面對紀律聆訊。"},{"pid":"8e0204d82f7a1ebcbe9072a1ac8a7ef8fc12d5a9","tid":309503,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T05:34:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56916118&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170705\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56916118%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170705&d=ZETiPhJ0t%2B%2BGroWVQ6EUKTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=17510f75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56916118%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170705&h=9f0c221c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56916118&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170705</a>"},{"pid":"27ba50e6a9cf666e3e1b9ea554661e649e64b39b","tid":309503,"uid":3117,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T05:36:03.000Z","msg":"2000就算？起碼都入去坐啦 睇個樣都知係食屎狗"},{"pid":"a2ade39859b430eb2